title: BONUS: Mail plus First Live Stream
description:
Here's an upload of our first live stream on 11/13/21!  Thanks to every one who made it.  The video version is available on YouTube, However, the audio quality wasn't perfect so sorry about that!  This was just as much a test run as anything, so don't worry if you missed out, we'll stream more in the future!
 
Thanks for Judging with us :)
